channel.title: Squeak/ring
channel.description:
My computer sometimes gives off a squeak/ringing noise on the inside. It is usually triggered by weird things.
Once the squeak would happen everytime i scrolled through a pdf but now its gone
the ringing happened today when I played a youtube video.
does anyone know what could be wrong? I think it is probably some fan.
